    </TablixRows></TablixBody><TablixColumnHierarchy><TablixMembers><TablixMember /><TablixMember /><TablixMember /><TablixMember /><TablixMember /><TablixMember /><TablixMember /></TablixMembers></TablixColumnHierarchy><TablixRowHierarchy><TablixMembers><TablixMember><KeepWithGroup>After</KeepWithGroup><RepeatOnNewPage>true</RepeatOnNewPage></TablixMember><TablixMember><Group Name="DetailsGroup" /></TablixMember></TablixMembers></TablixRowHierarchy><DataSetName>DataSet_Result</DataSetName><Top>3.25in</Top><Left>0in</Left><Height>0.68in</Height><Width>7.8in</Width><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>7.4pt</FontSize></Style></Tablix>
    <Textbox Name="Totals"><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>="Subtotal      " &amp; Format(First(Fields!SubtotalAmount.Value,"DataSet_Result"),"N2")</Value></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Right</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>="Sales Tax      " &amp; Format(First(Fields!TaxAmount.Value,"DataSet_Result"),"N2")</Value></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Right</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>="Order Total      " &amp; Format(First(Fields!OrderTotalAmount.Value,"DataSet_Result"),"N2")</Value><Style><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Right</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph></Paragraphs><Top>4.70in</Top><Left>5.15in</Left><Height>0.68in</Height><Width>2.65in</Width><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize><Border><Style>None</Style></Border></Style></Textbox>
    <Textbox Name="PrepaymentRequired"><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>=Format(First(Fields!PrepaymentPercent.Value,"DataSet_Result"),"0.##") &amp; "% Prepayment Required"</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>12pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph></Paragraphs><Top>5.45in</Top><Left>1.35in</Left><Height>0.3in</Height><Width>5.1in</Width><Style><Border><Style>None</Style></Border></Style></Textbox>
    <Textbox Name="AmountDue"><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>Prepayment Amount Due   </Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>12pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value>="$" &amp; Format(First(Fields!PrepaymentAmountDue.Value,"DataSet_Result"),"N2")</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>12pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph></Paragraphs><Top>5.80in</Top><Left>1.1in</Left><Height>0.32in</Height><Width>5.6in</Width><Style><Border><Style>None</Style></Border></Style></Textbox>
    <Textbox Name="Instructions"><CanGrow>true</CanGrow><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>Upon shipment, a final invoice will be sent. Deduct the amount prepaid from the invoice total.</Value><Style><Color>Red</Color><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>Gamer Packaging is pleased to offer several payment options.</Value><Style><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>Please visit the payments page on our website for more information:</Value><Style><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>https://www.gamerpackaging.com/payment-instructions/</Value><Style><Color>#0563C1</Color><TextDecoration>Underline</TextDecoration><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>* Payments made by credit card are subject to an administrative surcharge.</Value><Style><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph></Paragraphs><Top>6.18in</Top><Left>0.2in</Left><Height>1.10in</Height><Width>7.4in</Width><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8.5pt</FontSize><Border><Style>None</Style></Border></Style></Textbox>
    <Textbox Name="Contact"><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>=First(Fields!ContactLine.Value,"DataSet_Result")</Value><Style><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph></Paragraphs><Top>7.42in</Top><Left>0in</Left><Height>0.25in</Height><Width>7.8in</Width><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8.5pt</FontSize><Border><Style>None</Style></Border></Style></Textbox>
    <Textbox Name="Footer"><CanGrow>true</CanGrow><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>This offer is subject to the Standard Terms and Conditions of Gamer Packaging, Inc. which is set forth on our website:</Value><Style><FontStyle>Italic</FontStyle><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>https://www.gamerpackaging.com/terms-conditions-customer-sales/</Value><Style><Color>#0563C1</Color><TextDecoration>Underline</TextDecoration></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>=First(Fields!CompanyName.Value,"DataSet_Result") &amp; " | " &amp; First(Fields!CompanyAddress.Value,"DataSet_Result") &amp; IIF(First(Fields!CompanyAddress2.Value,"DataSet_Result")="",""," " &amp; First(Fields!CompanyAddress2.Value,"DataSet_Result")) &amp; ", " &amp; First(Fields!CompanyCity.Value,"DataSet_Result") &amp; ", " &amp; First(Fields!CompanyState.Value,"DataSet_Result") &amp; " " &amp; First(Fields!CompanyPostCode.Value,"DataSet_Result") &amp; " | " &amp; First(Fields!CompanyPhone.Value,"DataSet_Result") &amp; " | " &amp; First(Fields!CompanyHomePage.Value,"DataSet_Result")</Value><Style><FontSize>7pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Center</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph></Paragraphs><Top>7.73in</Top><Left>0in</Left><Height>0.68in</Height><Width>7.8in</Width><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>7.5pt</FontSize><Border><Style>None</Style></Border></Style></Textbox>
